#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.view"
msgstr "# triton.language.view"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:4
msgid "创建张量的视图，改变形状但不复制数据，类似于reshape，但更强调视图的概念，保持数据在内存中的连续性。"
msgstr "Create a view of a tensor, changing its shape without copying data, similar to `reshape`, but with a stronger emphasis on the concept of a view, maintaining the continuity of data in memory."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.view(input, shape)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `input.view(shape)` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.view(input, shape)` - function call form\n"
"- `input.view(shape)` - member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Function:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:12
msgid ""
"- 创建张量的视图，改变形状但不复制数据\n"
"- 类似于reshape，但更强调视图的概念\n"
"- 保持数据在内存中的连续性\n"
msgstr ""
"- Create a view of a tensor, changing its shape without copying the data  \n"
"- Similar to `reshape`, but with a stronger emphasis on the concept of a view  \n"
"- Maintains the contiguity of data in memory\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | 是 | 输入张量 |\n"
"| shape | List[int] | 是 | 目标形状 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|----------------|------|----------|-------------|\n"
"| input | tensor | Yes | Input tensor |\n"
"| shape | List[int] | Yes | Target shape |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 与shape参数指定的目标形状相同\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 与输入张量在内存中连续\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor\n"
"- **Shape:** Same as the target shape specified by the `shape` parameter\n"
"- **Data type:** Same as the input tensor\n"
"- **Memory layout:** Contiguous in memory with the input tensor\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:24
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/view.md:26
msgid ""
"- 输入和输出张量的总元素数必须相等\n"
"- 输出张量必须与输入张量在内存中连续\n"
msgstr ""
"- The total number of elements in the input and output tensors must be equal\n"
"- The output tensor must be contiguous in memory with the input tensor\n"

